Replaces: python3-distgpio
Conflicts: python3-distgpio
Description: A distributed no-master key-value store
 DistGPIO is a link between GPIO pins and DistKV.
 .
 It can write values that it reads from GPIO to some DistKV entry, monitor a
 DistKV entry and write any updates to a GPIO pin, and work with DistKV's runner
 system, either centrally or distributed.
